#: ../../J/Jeff-K-.rst:5
msgid "Jeff K."
msgstr "Jeff K."

#: ../../J/Jeff-K-.rst:7
msgid ""
"The spiritual successor to :ref:`B1FF` and the archetype of :ref:`script-"
"kiddies`\\. Jeff K. is a sixteen-year-old suburbanite who fancies himself a "
"\"l33t haX0r\", although his knowledge of computers seems to be limited to "
"the procedure for getting Quake up and running. His Web page "
"`http://www.somethingawful.com/jeffk/ "
"<http://www.somethingawful.com/jeffk/>`_\\  features a number of hopelessly "
"naive articles, essays, and rants, all filled with the kind of misspellings,"
" :ref:`studlycaps`\\, and number-for-letter substitutions endemic to the "
"script kiddie and :ref:`warez-d00dz` communities. Jeff's offerings, among "
"other things, include hardware advice (such as \"AMD VERSIS PENTIUM\" and "
"\"HOW TO OVARCLOAK YOUR COMPUTAR\"), his own Quake clan (Clan 40 OUNSCE), "
"and his own comic strip (Wacky Fun Computar Comic Jokes)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`B1FF`\\ の精神的後継者であり、\\ :ref:`script-kiddies`\\ の原型。Jeff K.は自分を「l33t "
"haX0r(エリートハッカー)」だと思い込んでいる16歳の郊外住まいの少年だが、彼のコンピュータの知識はQuakeを起動して動かす手順に限られているようだ。彼のWebページ"
" `http://www.somethingawful.com/jeffk/ "
"<http://www.somethingawful.com/jeffk/>`_\\ "
"には、救いようのないほど世間知らずな記事、エッセイ、わめき散らしが多数掲載されており、そのすべてがスクリプトキディや\\ "
":ref:`warez-d00dz`\\ コミュニティに特有のスペルミス、\\ :ref:`studlycaps`\\ "
"、文字を数字に置き換える表記で埋め尽くされている。Jeffの提供物には、とりわけハードウェアのアドバイス(「AMD VERSIS "
"PENTIUM」や「HOW TO OVARCLOAK YOUR COMPUTAR」など)、彼自身のQuakeクラン(Clan 40 "
"OUNSCE)、彼自身のコミックストリップ(Wacky Fun Computar Comic Jokes)などがある。"

#: ../../J/Jeff-K-.rst:12
msgid ""
"Like B1FF, Jeff K. is (fortunately) a hoax. Jeff K. was created by internet "
"game journalist Richard \"Lowtax\" Kyanka, whose web site Something Awful "
"(http://www.somethingawful.com) highlights unintentionally humorous news "
"items and Web sites, as a parody of the kind of teenage :ref:`luser` who "
"infests Quake servers, chat rooms, and other places where computer "
"enthusiasts congregate. He is well-recognized in the PC game community and "
"his influence has spread to hacker :ref:`fora` like Slashdot as well."
msgstr ""
"B1FFと同様、Jeff K.は(幸いにも)でっち上げである。Jeff K.は、インターネットのゲームジャーナリストRichard \"Lowtax\""
" Kyankaによって作られた。彼のウェブサイトSomething "
"Awful(http://www.somethingawful.com)は、意図せず笑える時事ネタやWebサイトを取り上げており、Quakeサーバーやチャットルーム、その他コンピュータ愛好家が集まる場所にはびこる類のティーンエイジの\\"
" :ref:`luser`\\ のパロディとして作られた。彼はPCゲームコミュニティでよく知られており、その影響はSlashdotのようなハッカーの\\"
" :ref:`fora`\\ にまで広がっている。"
